usage_guide.note:
There are a number of stepmod modules that AP233 needs to view as being part of 
      product data management and available for use by the 2 second tier modules.  
      For example:     

USE FROM Experience_arm;

USE FROM Information_product_arm;

USE FROM Information_rights_arm;

USE FROM Justification_arm;

USE FROM Organization_type_arm;

USE FROM Position_in_organization_arm;

USE FROM Qualifications_arm;

USE FROM Type_of_person_arm;
	  How and where these and other needed-by-all modules get inserted into the 
	  schema framework is to be determined.
